{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t4-train-5","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"有理数","title":"针对训练5：绝对值综合问题","difficulty":5,"tags":["绝对值","综合"],"content":"若 $|a| = 3$，$|b| = 5$，$|a + b| = a + b$，求 $a - b$ 的值。","steps":[{"title":"分析条件","content":"$|a + b| = a + b$ 表示 $a + b \\geq 0$\n\n$|a| = 3 \\Rightarrow a = \\pm 3$\n\n$|b| = 5 \\Rightarrow b = \\pm 5$","formula":"a + b \\geq 0"},{"title":"分类讨论","content":"满足 $a + b \\geq 0$ 的情况：\n\n① $a = 3$，$b = 5$：$a + b = 8 \\geq 0$ ✓，$a - b = -2$\n\n② $a = 3$，$b = -5$：$a + b = -2 < 0$ ✗\n\n③ $a = -3$，$b = 5$：$a + b = 2 \\geq 0$ ✓，$a - b = -8$\n\n④ $a = -3$，$b = -5$：$a + b = -8 < 0$ ✗","formula":"a - b = -2 \\text{ 或 } a - b = -8"}]},"id":"t4-train-5"},"__N_SSG":true}